wiki.text:
'Pide' may refer to:

*Pita, Turkish version of a type of flatbread consumed especially in company of
kebabs *PIDE ("Polícia Internacional e de Defesa do Estado or PIDE" -
International and State Defense Police; later renamed "Direcção-Geral de
Segurança" - General Security Directorate), the political secret police during
the authoritarian Portuguese regime of the Estado Novo *Pakistan Institute of
Development Economics, established by Government of Pakistan for developing the
status of economy *Pide (dish), a plate of the Turkish cuisine, consisting of a
dough variety similar to that of "Pide" (Turkish version of pita) with toppings
or fillings like meat, cheese, spinach, pastirma, eggs etc and baked altogether
in a traditional bakery oven
